### Service Management

**Check Status:**
```powershell
.\install-service.ps1 -Status
```

**Stop Service:**
```powershell
.\install-service.ps1 -Stop
```

**Start Service:**
```powershell
.\install-service.ps1 -Start
```

**Uninstall Service:**
```powershell
.\install-service.ps1 -Uninstall
```

**View Live Logs:**
```powershell
Get-Content logs\chimera-stdout.log -Tail 50 -Wait
```

**View Error Logs:**
```powershell
Get-Content logs\chimera-stderr.log -Tail 50
```

